1
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:08,132
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,260 --> 00:01:11,172
=Episode 15=

3
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:20,959
Your Highness.

4
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:23,439
How's it?

5
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:25,799
Her Majesty is safe.

6
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,000
We're discovered?

7
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,879
Lady Liang confessed herself.

8
00:01:32,359 --> 00:01:35,840
I heard Prince Xiaoyao gave Xu Jun
control of the capital guards overnight.

9
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:39,439
And Lady Liang's father
is now under Xu Jun's protection.

10
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,239
And...

11
00:01:45,319 --> 00:01:46,840
The Marquis of Zhenbei fears failure.

12
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,359
He plans to act early.

13
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:53,519
He thinks threatening the life
of Lady Liang's father

14
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:57,439
is how he can get her
to poison the Empress.

15
00:01:57,959 --> 00:02:00,000
He outsmarts himself.

16
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,480
He's a useless pawn now.

17
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:06,719
Now, we must find a way
to prevent him from implicating us.

18
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,319
Keep a close watch
on the border and the capital.

19
00:02:09,719 --> 00:02:12,000
I need to carefully consider

20
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:16,039
how to proceed with the next move.

21
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,020
Yes.

22
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,159
Does it hurt?

23
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:38,800
No.

24
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:42,120
But you're already a dead person.

25
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,280
Your Majesty.

26
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,479
You can still smile?

27
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:58,800
I thought you were virtuous,

28
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,639
so you were named Virtuous Consort.

29
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,120
But now, it seems

30
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:04,840
Reckless Consort would suit you better.

31
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,520
Impulsive and reckless.

32
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,719
Xu Yu.

33
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:14,159
Even in this miserable state,
you're still so arrogant?

34
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,560
Rot in the Cold Palace.

35
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:17,879
What?

36
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:20,840
It seems like you're here for revenge?

37
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:22,240
Revenge?

38
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:26,919
The harem is much duller
without you as an opponent.

39
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,159
I'm here

40
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,199
to toy with you.

41
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:33,560
Since you're here, you're a criminal.

42
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,560
Having dragon
and phoenix patterns? How improper!

43
00:03:37,479 --> 00:03:38,560
Remove all these things!

44
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:44,960
Move faster!

45
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,639
Take this couch away too!

46
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:47,280
Yes.

47
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,400
Not even the bed?

48
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:58,560
The bed has dragon and phoenix carvings.

49
00:03:58,919 --> 00:04:00,400
Then it must be removed.

50
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:05,199
You're doing
an excellent job as Consort.

51
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:07,680
Whoever betrays His Majesty

52
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,639
is my enemy.

53
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,439
Didn't I leave you a table and chairs?

54
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,560
Be grateful.

55
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:26,600
(It seems heaven also
seeks justice for Xu Yu,)

56
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,680
(letting me taste
the bitterness of karma.)

57
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,839
Your Majesty!

58
00:04:35,079 --> 00:04:36,199
Your Majesty.

59
00:04:37,439 --> 00:04:39,399
It's all my fault.

60
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:43,199
In the future, leave
all such menial tasks to me.

61
00:04:44,199 --> 00:04:48,399
I brought your personal maid, Xuan.

62
00:04:48,579 --> 00:04:49,079
Here.

63
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:49,800
Go.

64
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:54,240
Xuan, take good care of Her Majesty.

65
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,839
Your Highness.

66
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:06,319
You've caused big trouble!

67
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,959
I'm seeking justice for His Majesty!

68
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,839
Unlike you,

69
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:13,319
bringing food to that wretch again.

70
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,160
With Her Majesty in trouble now,

71
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,879
you shouldn't kick her while she's down.

72
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,399
Instead, support her.

73
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:22,279
That wretch had an affair
with Prince Xiaoyao!

74
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:25,079
She practically trampled
His Majesty's dignity!

75
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:26,639
And you want to help her?

76
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:30,040
What if the one in the Cold Palace now

77
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,879
isn't Her Majesty,

78
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,240
but His Majesty?

79
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,480
What do you mean?

80
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:36,759
Let me tell you.

81
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,839
(Lady Liang is right.)

82
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,480
(Caution ensures a long life.)

83
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,000
(If this one is His Majesty,)

84
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,639
(being so near,
I'd have a big advantage.)

85
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:57,079
Thank you for your hard work.

86
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:59,720
Since entering the palace
many years ago,

87
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,160
my only wish has been

88
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:04,519
His Majesty's health

89
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,079
and heirs.

90
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:09,800
If you miss His Majesty so much,

91
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:11,720
you should go to the border to find him.

92
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,519
Why come to this Cold Palace?

93
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,800
Precisely because His Majesty is away,

94
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:23,959
I should attend to you, Your Majesty.

95
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:34,800
Is the pressure alright?

96
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,720
(Am I going crazy?)

97
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:48,160
(Why does she seem
more beautiful the longer I look?)

98
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,279
(No!)

99
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:51,839
(In His Majesty's eyes,
only I must be the fairest.)

100
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,879
(I must seize this chance
to prove my loyalty.)

101
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,959
Your Majesty, you must be wronged.

102
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:08,560
If there's anything I can do,

103
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,639
just let me know.

104
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,519
Alright.

105
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,120
In that case,

106
00:07:12,959 --> 00:07:14,639
I need you to deliver a message for me

107
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:16,439
to Prince Xiaoyao and Physician Jiang.

108
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:22,720
Your Majesty.

109
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:25,319
There may be dangers along this journey.

110
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:28,079
Xu Duo will always be by your side.

111
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:30,879
Please be cautious

112
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:31,959
and return safely.

113
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,279
May the world be at peace.

114
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:40,279
May you return safely.

115
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,000
See you in the capital.

116
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,439
See you in the capital.

117
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,360
Please stay.

118
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:53,779
Huna.

119
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,439
Why not tell me you are leaving?

120
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:01,240
It's late at night.
No need to bother you.

121
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:03,040
It is bitterly cold now.

122
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:06,399
How will you withstand this blizzard
and cross the Tianshan Mountains?

123
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:10,000
The Empress has written to me.

124
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,720
If she summons me,

125
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,720
I will come to her, no matter how far.

126
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,879
Dada has submitted
a state letter to Chen.

127
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:19,584
We pledge allegiance to Chen.

128
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,720
I hope you will do the same for Dada.

129
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,759
If you summon us, we'll come to you,

130
00:08:23,759 --> 00:08:24,759
no matter how far.

131
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:26,800
Very well.

132
00:08:27,199 --> 00:08:28,480
This is my promise to you.

133
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:39,720
Set out!

134
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:43,200
Duo.

135
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,799
Protect His Majesty.

136
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:45,480
Yes, Father.

137
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,759
He is the Emperor of Chen.

138
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:57,399
Is it worth it?

139
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,200
If the eagle of the grasslands
flies high enough,

140
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:02,399
it can reach the mountains

141
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,360
and descend into snow pools.

142
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,759
And it can also reach

143
00:09:07,279 --> 00:09:08,320
the capital of Chen.

144
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:18,980
Giddyap.

145
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,340
Giddyap.

146
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:20,940
Giddyap.

147
00:09:21,419 --> 00:09:21,919
Giddyap.

148
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,419
Giddyap.

149
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,100
Giddyap.

150
00:09:24,019 --> 00:09:24,519
Giddyap.

151
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:25,019
Giddyap.

152
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:26,799
Your Majesty!

153
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,440
I have something to report!

154
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:30,784
Your Majesty.

155
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:33,240
We've been traveling
nonstop for three days.

156
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,399
Even a few horses have died.

157
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,320
And the men are exhausted.

158
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:40,360
I believe we should stop
to rest before continuing.

159
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,039
Soldiers,

160
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:53,639
you will rest here.

161
00:09:54,019 --> 00:09:55,200
I will go ahead.

162
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:56,220
No, Your Majesty!

163
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,519
Don't do so!

164
00:09:57,679 --> 00:09:59,200
Let me scout ahead instead

165
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,120
for Your Majesty.

166
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:00,679
No need.

167
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:03,039
Inside the palace,
it's more dangerous than here.

168
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,960
Xu Yu is waiting for me.

169
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:06,840
That's an order.

170
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:07,879
Your Majesty!

171
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,279
Your Majesty!

172
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:15,159
(Xiao Jinyun, wait for me.)

173
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:21,519
(Xu Yu.)

174
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:24,159
(Where are you now?)

175
00:10:24,639 --> 00:10:25,840
(I really miss you.)

176
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,360
(Your Majesty.)

177
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,159
I am overthinking again.

178
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,399
I always hear Xu Yu's voice.

179
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,000
Xiao Jinyun!

180
00:10:56,128 --> 00:10:58,144
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

181
00:10:58,336 --> 00:11:02,080
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

182
00:11:02,656 --> 00:11:07,328
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

183
00:11:07,872 --> 00:11:09,632
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

184
00:11:09,952 --> 00:11:13,568
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

185
00:11:13,815 --> 00:11:19,342
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪

186
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:21,600
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

187
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:25,920
♪All who believed love would never fade♪

188
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:31,008
♪The wind scatters countless sorrows♪

189
00:11:31,008 --> 00:11:33,056
♪Like a song, like a dream, like a play♪

190
00:11:33,056 --> 00:11:37,208
♪This life is but a solitary boat♪

191
00:11:37,208 --> 00:11:43,520
♪No one ferries me
across this sea of pain♪

192
00:11:54,712 --> 00:11:59,159
♪Fate tears us apart♪

193
00:11:59,159 --> 00:11:59,960
Xu Yu.

194
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,480
You're finally back.

195
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:04,720
It's me.

196
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:06,879
I'm back.

197
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,039
Great.

198
00:12:09,248 --> 00:12:11,264
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

199
00:12:11,456 --> 00:12:15,200
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

200
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:21,422
♪No one ferries me
across this sea of pain♪

201
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,152
Virtuous Consort
wrote this letter to us.

202
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:32,799
It lists all suspicious food
and items recorded by Her Majesty.

203
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:37,039
Sorcery.

204
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:40,639
(Talismans and Spirits)
It can fake Her Majesty's pregnancy.

205
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:46,419
Here.

206
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:50,840
These are stamens I gathered
from various trees beyond the frontier.

207
00:12:51,639 --> 00:12:53,799
They say these trees
only grow in the desert,

208
00:12:53,799 --> 00:12:55,159
which are rare in Central Plains.

209
00:12:55,159 --> 00:12:58,000
Through your body,
I've experienced countless adventures.

210
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:01,639
Now, I want you to feel
the desert's essence.

211
00:13:11,759 --> 00:13:12,600
Let me take a look.

212
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,279
You've tanned

213
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,159
and grown thinner.

214
00:13:20,279 --> 00:13:21,440
Desert blizzards

215
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,799
and battlefield clashes,

216
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:23,879
what exhilaration!

217
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:24,919
Next time,

218
00:13:25,039 --> 00:13:25,879
I'll go again.

219
00:13:30,159 --> 00:13:31,159
No next time.

220
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:34,200
I'll never let you
take such risks again.

221
00:13:36,039 --> 00:13:36,759
And you?

222
00:13:37,279 --> 00:13:38,960
You endured injustice,
but sent me no word.

223
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,519
If Jinming hadn't told me,

224
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,440
I'd never have learned

225
00:13:42,879 --> 00:13:44,279
you were cast into the Cold Palace.

226
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,879
Tell me what truly happened.

227
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:49,919
I...

228
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,000
I was falsely accused of pregnancy.

229
00:13:54,279 --> 00:13:55,720
To save my life,

230
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:57,344
Jinming was forced to claim paternity.

231
00:14:07,559 --> 00:14:10,679
Your Majesty...
Your Majesty, as the supreme ruler,

232
00:14:10,919 --> 00:14:12,879
you suffered such injustice.

233
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:18,200
It must be Marquis of Zhenbei's doing.

234
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:20,320
I'll execute him this instant!

235
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:23,639
The Supreme Court has gathered
ample evidence against him.

236
00:14:24,159 --> 00:14:25,000
He won't escape.

237
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,279
But you...

238
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,159
After your arduous journey,

239
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,840
you should rest now.

240
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:34,320
The Chen Emperor's might now echoes
across the nations beyond the frontier.

241
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:35,679
Rest easy.

242
00:14:36,159 --> 00:14:37,639
They're at your mercy.

243
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,840
You can deal with them in any way.

244
00:14:41,039 --> 00:14:41,639
Xu Yu.

245
00:14:42,919 --> 00:14:44,279
All credit belongs to you.

246
00:14:48,159 --> 00:14:49,080
And to Your Majesty.

247
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,200
Now that I've returned,

248
00:15:01,159 --> 00:15:03,000
I will clear your name.

249
00:15:22,244 --> 00:15:27,428
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

250
00:15:28,164 --> 00:15:32,727
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

251
00:15:34,052 --> 00:15:39,467
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

252
00:15:40,036 --> 00:15:44,580
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

253
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:50,484
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

254
00:15:50,852 --> 00:15:56,529
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

255
00:15:56,868 --> 00:15:58,884
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

256
00:15:59,076 --> 00:16:02,820
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

257
00:16:03,396 --> 00:16:08,068
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

258
00:16:08,612 --> 00:16:10,372
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

259
00:16:10,692 --> 00:16:14,308
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

260
00:16:14,555 --> 00:16:20,082
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
